    </para>
    <para condition="html" role="usernotes">Notes utilisateur :
      <ulink url="&blfs-wiki;/telepathy-logger"/>
    </para>
  </sect2>
  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de Telepathy Logger</title>
    <para>
      Install <application>Telepathy Logger</application> by running the
      following  
    </para>
<screen>
<userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr \
            --libexecdir=/usr/lib/telepathy \
            --disable-static &amp;&amp;
make</userinput>
</screen>
    <para>
      Pour tester le résultat, tapez : <command>make check</command>.
    </para>
    <para>
      Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> :
    </para>
<screen role="root">
<userinput>make install</userinput>
</screen>
  </sect2>
